---

<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>Yiming - Senior Software Engineer</title>
		<meta name="description" content="Personal portfolio of Yiming, Senior Software Engineer at WetaFx Ltd" />
		<style>
			body {
				font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
				line-height: 1.6;
				max-width: 800px;
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 2rem;
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
				min-height: 100vh;
				color: #333;
			}
			
			.container {
				background: white;
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 3rem;
				box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
			}
			
			.header {
				text-align: center;
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
			}
			
			.name {
				font-size: 3rem;
				font-weight: 700;
				margin: 0;
				background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
				-webkit-background-clip: text;
				-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
				background-clip: text;
			}
			
			.title {
				font-size: 1.5rem;
				color: #666;
				margin: 0.5rem 0;
			}
			
			.company {
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				color: #888;
				margin: 0;
			}
			
			.intro {
				font-size: 1.1rem;
				line-height: 1.8;
				margin: 2rem 0;
				text-align: center;
			}
			
			.linkedin-link {
				color: #0077b5;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 600;
			}
			
			.linkedin-link:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
			
			.tech-stack {
				margin-top: 3rem;
			}
			
			.tech-stack h2 {
				color: #333;
				border-bottom: 2px solid #667eea;
				padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
			}
			
			.tech-list {
				list-style: none;
				padding: 0;
			}
			
			.tech-list li {
				background: #f8f9fa;
				margin: 0.5rem 0;
				padding: 1rem;
				border-radius: 8px;
				border-left: 4px solid #667eea;
			}
			
			.tech-list a {
				color: #667eea;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 600;
			}
			
			.tech-list a:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
			
			.status {
				background: #e8f5e8;
				border: 1px solid #4caf50;
				border-radius: 8px;
				padding: 1rem;
				margin: 2rem 0;
				text-align: center;
				color: #2e7d32;
			}
			
			@media (max-width: 600px) {
				body {
					padding: 1rem;
				}
				
				.container {
					padding: 2rem;
				}
				
				.name {
					font-size: 2rem;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<div class="container">
			<header class="header">
				<h1 class="name">Yiming</h1>
				<p class="title">Senior Software Engineer</p>
				<p class="company">WetaFx Ltd</p>
			</header>
			
			<main>
				<div class="intro">
					<p>Hello, welcome to my home page!</p>
					<p>
						I am <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/yiming-nz/" class="linkedin-link" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Yiming</a>, 
						currently working as a senior software engineer at WetaFx Ltd.
					</p>
					<p>
						You might have seen my old home page built about 7 years ago, which is clearly much outdated, 
						so I am currently working on rebuilding this new page.
					</p>
				</div>
				
				<div class="status">
					ðŸš§ This website is currently under construction using modern web technologies!
				</div>
				
				<section class="tech-stack">
					<h2>New Tech Stack</h2>
					<ul class="tech-list">
						<li>
							<strong><a href="https://astro.new/latest/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Astro.new</a></strong>
							- Modern static site generator for fast, content-focused websites
						</li>
						<li>
							<strong>GitHub Actions</strong>
							- Automated deployment and CI/CD pipeline
						</li>
					</ul>
				</section>
			</main>
		</div>
	</body>
</html>
